code: import PackageJSON from'../../../package.json';async function LoginUser(email,password,setError){var url='';if(PackageJSON.API.DebugMode)url=PackageJSON.API.BaseURLDebug+PackageJSON.API.Login;else url=PackageJSON.API.BaseURLProd+PackageJSON.API.Login;const model={email:email,password:password};const modelJson=JSON.stringify(model);try{const response=await fetch(url,{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},credentials:'include',body:modelJson});const json=await response.json();if(response.status===400&&json!==null&&json.Error!==null){setError(json.Error);return null;}if(!response.ok)return null;return json;}catch(e){return[];}}export default LoginUser;
